#### 2

[metadata]
title = "Chapter II. Judgment of Divines and grave Authors concerning Enthusiasm――Reflections upon Scepticism――A Sceptick-Christian――Judgment of the Inspir'd concerning their own Inspirations――Knowledg and Belief――History of Religion resum'd――Zeal Offensive and Defensive――A Church in Danger――Persecution――Policy of the Church of Rome"
